[{"Id": 1016640, "EnglishTitle": "PLEASE NOTE: Be it clear that the reason for presenting Translation is to understand Salaat and to recite in Arabic with concentration because reciting Salaat other than Arabic language (or Transliteration) is not correct.", "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": "Waazeh rahe keh tarjuma-e-namaz pesh karne ki asal wajah namaz samajh ke Arabi mein khuzoo aur tawajjoh ke saath namaz padhna hai. Kyu’n keh Arabi ya Roman-Arabi (Transliteration) ke siwa kisi aur zabaan mein namaz padhna sahih nahin hai.", "UrduTitle": "واضح رہے کہ ترجمۂ نماز پیش کرنے کی اصل غرض نماز سمجھ کے عربی میں خضوع اور توجہ کے ساتھ نماز پڑھنا ہے۔ کیوں کہ عربی کے سوا کسی اور زبان میں نماز پڑھنا صحیح نہیں ہے۔ اس لئے ہر ایک کے لئے نماز کی حد تک قرآن و عربی سیکھنا واجب ہے۔", "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1017584, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "Sayyid ibn Tawoos, in his book of al-Mazar, Chapter: Rites of Kufah Mosque, after mentioning the recommended acts at Imam Ali’s Niche (mehraab), has mentioned a special prayer for settling the needs to be offered there. This prayer consists of 4 units in the form of 2x2 units. In the 1st rakat, after <Surah Fateha> recite <Surah Ikhlaas> 10 times. In the 2nd rakat, after <Surah Fateha> recite <Surah Ikhlaas> 21 times. In the 3rd rakat, after <Surah Fateha> recite <Surah Ikhlaas> 10 times and in the 4th rakat, after <Surah Fateha> recite <Surah Ikhlaas> 41 times. After namaz recite Tasbeeh-e-Zahra (s), then recite <Surah Ikhlaas> 51 times and then say 50 times…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Sayyed ibne Tawoos ne apni kitaab Al-Mazaar mein Masjid-e-Kufa mein Mehraab-e-Ameerul Momeneen (a) ke amaal mein ek Namaz-e-Haajat ka zikr farmaya hai khusoosi taur par wohi adaa ki jaati hai aur woh 4 rakat jo 2-2 kar ke padhi jaati hai, iski 1st rakat mein <Surah Fateha> ke baad 10 martaba <Surah Ikhlaas> aur 2nd rakat mein <Surah Fateha> ke baad 21 martaba <Surah Ikhlaas>, 3rd rakat mein <Surah Fateha> ke baad 31 martaba <Surah Ikhlaas> aur 4th rakat mein <Surah Fateha> ke baad 41 martaba <Surah Ikhlaas> padhi jaati hai. Salaam ke baad Tasbeeh-e-Zahra (s) padhe, phir 51 martaba <Surah Ikhlaas> padhe aur 50 martaba kahe…", "UrduDescription": "سیدابن طاؤس ؒ نے اپنی کتاب ’’المزار ‘‘ میں مسجد کوفہ میں محراب امیر المومنینؑ کے اعمال میں ایک نماز حاجت کا ذکر فرمایا ہے جو خصوصی طور پر وہیں ادا کی جاتی ہے اور وہ ۴رکعت جو ۲ سلام کے ساتھ بجا لائی جاتی ہے اس کی پہلی رکعت میں <سورۂ فاتحہ> کے بعد ۱۰ مرتبہ <سورۂ اخلاص> اور دوسری رکعت میں <سورۂ فاتحہ> کے بعد ۲۱ مرتبہ <سورۂ اخلاص> تیسری رکعت میں <سورۂ فاتحہ> کے بعد۳۱ مرتبہ <سورۂ اخلاص> اور چوتھی رکعت میں <سورۂ فاتحہ> کے بعد ۴۱ مرتبہ <سورۂ اخلاص> پڑھی جاتی ہے سلام کے بعد تسبیح پڑھے پھر ۵۱ مرتبہ <سورۂ اخلاص> پڑھے اور ۵۰ مرتبہ کہے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "Arabi